'''謝拉·阿爾梅達·赫爾希'''（{{lang-en|'''Sheyla Almeida Hershey'''}}，{{bd|1979年|12月19日}}）是一位在[[巴西|巴西]]出生，現時在[[美國|美國]][[德薩斯州|德薩斯州]]首府[[侯斯頓|侯斯頓]]居住的[[模特兒|模特兒]]<ref name=myfoxhouston>{{cite news |url=http://www.myfoxhouston.com/dpp/health/100713-sheyla-hershey-breast-implants-infection |title=Bigger Implants Led to Breast Infection |publisher=My Fox Houston |date=2010-07-13 |language=en |title_zh=更大的植入物引致乳房發炎 |accessdate=2010-07-22 |author=[http://www.myfoxhouston.com/dpp/about_us/Melissa_Wilson Wilson, M.] |archive-date=2010-07-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100722094152/http://www.myfoxhouston.com/dpp/health/100713-sheyla-hershey-breast-implants-infection |dead-url=no }}</ref>。她本來只是一位普通家庭主婦，但後來因為不斷進行[[隆胸|隆胸]]手術，使她成為了「世界頭號人造波霸」<ref name=ifeng>{{cite news |url=http://news.ifeng.com/photo/hot/detail_2010_07/20/1803223_0.shtml |title=世界头号人造波霸乳房或将切除 |publisher=凤凰网 |date=2010-07-20 |accessdate=2010-07-22 |archive-date=2010-07-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100723190024/http://news.ifeng.com/photo/hot/detail_2010_07/20/1803223_0.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>。她在八年內經過三十多次手術後<ref name=ifeng />，把胸圍大增至34FFF<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.foxnews.com/story/0,2933,354431,00.html |title=Despite Risks, Woman Wants to Expand FFF Breasts | publisher=Fox News |date= May 2008 |language=en}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://abcnews.go.com/Health/PainManagement/story?id=4823025&page=1 |title=When Big Breasts Are a Big Pain |publisher=ABC News |date=May 2008 |language=en |accessdate=2010-07-21 |archive-date=2010-02-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100211065936/http://abcnews.go.com/Health/PainManagement/story?id=4823025&page=1 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2009年1月尾，當她從家鄉巴西再進行另一次手術，在每邊胸部分別植入了一個5.5公升的矽袋<ref name=terra>{{cite web |url=http://vidaeestilo.terra.com.br/homem/interna/0,,OI4412540-EI12827,00-coisas+que+voce+talvez+nao+saiba+sobre+seios.html |title=Terra: 10 coisas que você talvez não saiba sobre seios |title_zh=地球：你可能不知道的十個有關乳房的事實 |author=Claudio R. S. Pucci |language=pt |accessdate=2010-07-22 |archive-date=2010-05-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100508053649/http://vidaeestilo.terra.com.br/homem/interna/0,,OI4412540-EI12827,00-coisas+que+voce+talvez+nao+saiba+sobre+seios.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，令她的胸圍再增大至38KKK，成為世界上胸圍最大的女性<ref name=ifeng /><ref name=dailystar>{{cite web |url= http://www.dailystar.co.uk/news/view/67835/I-ve-got-the-world-s-biggest-boobs/ |title= Daily Star (UK) |date= Jan 2009 |language= en |accessdate= 2010-07-21 |archive-date= 2010-07-19 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20100719050914/http://www.dailystar.co.uk/news/view/67835/I-ve-got-the-world-s-biggest-boobs/ |dead-url= no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.nypost.com/seven/02042009/news/nationalnews/texas_woman_breaks_breast_implant_record_153538.htm |title=Texas Woman Breaks Beast Implant Record |publisher=NY Post |date=Feb 2009 |language=en |accessdate=2010-07-21 |archive-date=2009-08-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090814113517/http://www.nypost.com/seven/02042009/news/nationalnews/texas_woman_breaks_breast_implant_record_153538.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.foxnews.com/story/0,2933,488384,00.html |title=Woman Sets Breast Implants Record: 38KKK |publisher=Fox News |date=Feb 2009 |accessdate=2010-07-21 |archive-date=2010-07-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100717141354/http://www.foxnews.com/story/0,2933,488384,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，亦令她賺取了在電視台上鏡的機會，開始了她的模特兒生涯。

不過，這次隆胸手術似乎帶她帶來了災難。2010年7月14日，赫謝被發現一對乳房在手術後感染了可致命的[[葡萄球菌|葡萄球菌]]，引起併發症。雖然後來她把所有植入物移除，但估計感染可能令她原來的一對乳房亦同樣要切除<ref name=myfoxhouston />。不過兩星期後，併發症似乎停止了，令她可以繼續完成餘下的手術部驟，雖然期間因為併發症的困擾令她失眠及失去食慾<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.torontosun.com/news/world/2010/07/27/14841806.html |title=Model with triple K-cup breasts "doing fine" |publisher={{tsl|en|Toronto Sun|Toronto Sun}} |date=2010-07-27 |accessdate=2010-07-28 |archive-date=2010-07-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100729120215/http://www.torontosun.com/news/world/2010/07/27/14841806.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

謝拉·阿爾梅達·赫爾希已婚，她的丈夫是德勒克·赫爾希。

